{"books":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":[""],"article":{"title":"大字报诗——孤独者之歌","authors":["北京大学","邓贵介"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"text":"大字报诗——孤独者之歌","type":"title"},{"text":"北京大学邓贵介","type":"authors"},{"text":"（邓贵介：北京大学物理系学生）","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"我多感慨啊！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"他们为什么要赶走这颗赶不走的共产主义赤心！？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"有股恶劣的气流引起了一件偶然的事，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我被当作了×××，或者×××。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"笨重的脚镣，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"小巧的反面手铐，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"辱骂、耳光。………","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一天接着一天，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一个审问员接着一个审问员，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"在我面前","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"忙啊！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"忙啊！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我爱的审问员呀！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我恨的审问员呀！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我健壮，没关系，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我只怨你审问太轻率，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"随随便便逮捕，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"随随便便定罪，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"随随便便释放。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"×××　　×××","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"前年九月里的一天，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我又被押到很多人面前。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"他们","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"狂怒！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"咆哮！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"高呼！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“………”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一个人接着一个人，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一个突击队接着一个突击队。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"在我的眼前","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"转呀！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"转呀！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我多难过啊！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"——是前世做了什么孽，无罪受冤。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我多感动啊！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"——他们要坚决、澈底、到底，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"——他们显得忠诚、勇敢。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"×××　　×××","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"今年，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我再碰不到审问员，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"也再没被押到很多人面前。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"只遇到很多人，他们与我","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"点点头，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"瞪瞪眼，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"互不睬理……","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一个人接着一个人，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一个领导接着一个领导","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"在我面前","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"过去","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"过去","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我多难受啊！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"——他们还有什么理由让我孤独？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我多感慨啊！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"他们为什么不再审问？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"他们为什么不再坚决、澈底、到底","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"他们为什么要赶走这颗赶不走的共产主义赤心。","type":"paragraph"}],"comments":[],"origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":0,"page_end":0,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}